Package: AfriAtlas
Title: Create Species and Effort Maps from African Bird Atlas Project Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bello", family = "Adamu Danmallam", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "adamubello001@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7783-4351"))
Description: Tools for generating standardized species distribution maps and
    coverage (effort) maps using the African Bird Atlas Project (ABAP) API.
    It provides functions to visualize pentad-level sighting data and survey
    effort across various African countries, primarily relying on 'sf',
    'ggplot2', and 'rnaturalearth' for geospatial processing and plotting.
